{"tid":676074,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得肥媽而家煮既野齋睇都覺得怪","createTime":"2018-05-24T05:44:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T06:53:17.000Z","uid":103611,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"062719785358676f402f96f3f1d5dc4d57e331f5","tid":676074,"uid":103611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:44:00.000Z","msg":"之前有集整鮑魚<br />\n用成隻雞加金華火腿同瑤柱已經諗下都覺得濃味<br />\n仲要再加一堆蝦同成隻蟹落去燜<br />\n仲有一大斤排骨<br />\n第一次見人又雞又排骨又金華火腿仲要又蝦又蟹咁一煲過去燜飽魚<br />\n燜完出黎咩味都有？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/134331_381947612536a471270f3ffac4e37ab1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F134331_381947612536a471270f3ffac4e37ab1.png&h=a3907479&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/134332_9a92c6b18d0e52f97205ed96b52ef6e3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F134332_9a92c6b18d0e52f97205ed96b52ef6e3.png&h=2c9dabc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有佢煮咩都落幾圈麻油<br />\n麻油既味雖然香但都幾出<br />\n咁咪樣樣煮出黎都麻油味<br />\n有冇廚藝高手出黎comment下<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔識煮野"},{"pid":"00a3e6bfb7bc21e33853c3d15eb6fb498a787f0a","tid":676074,"uid":113830,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T06:20:40.000Z","msg":"所以咪食到佢自己咁肥囉"},{"pid":"b79fca745a2595fc4eff22706d45ed65fb07b73d","tid":676074,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T06:30:14.000Z","msg":"六號拍節目個排，都唔知要班幾多美極先夠"},{"pid":"d67f08ea261af21c2d7766b3fff3a68c6fda5425","tid":676074,"uid":67485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T06:31:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cfd3dc57c3112db6abe1639bd7020db92fd0a25a","tid":676074,"uid":73748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T06:33:02.000Z","msg":"佢出名求鳩其"},{"pid":"a5508a970ecf273c3e409d8a1b9f2c05a8c608e5","tid":676074,"uid":182445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score